  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个内容社区的数据库结构，核心是有用户、帖子、标签这三块。用户能发帖子，帖子可以打多个标签。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USERS",
        "POSTS",
        "TAGS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那用户和帖子是一对多的关系吗？一个用户可以发多条帖子？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USERS",
        "POSTS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，一个用户对应多条帖子。帖子这边需要记录作者ID、标题、描述，还有个图片URL字段。另外帖子有个可见性设置，用枚举类型，比如公开、仅好友、私密。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "POSTS",
        "author_id",
        "title",
        "description",
        "image_url",
        "visibility"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在POSTS实体里加上这些字段，visibility用enum类型。那标签这边呢，只需要ID和名称吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TAGS",
        "id",
        "name"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "标签比较简单，就一个name字段，需要唯一约束。关键是帖子和标签是多对多关系，得有个关联表POST_TAGS。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TAGS",
        "name",
        "POST_TAGS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "POST_TAGS用复合主键，post_id和tag_id都是外键对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "POST_TAGS",
        "post_id",
        "tag_id"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。接下来是评论功能，COMMENTS表要有评论ID、所属帖子ID、作者ID、评论内容，还要记录点赞数。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMMENTS",
        "post_id",
