      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "两个都要。like_count是冗余计数方便查询，但还需要COMMENT_LIKES记录谁点了赞，防止重复点赞。这个表用comment_id和user_id做联合外键。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMMENTS",
        "like_count",
        "COMMENT_LIKES",
        "comment_id",
        "user_id"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "了解了，COMMENT_LIKES记录点赞人和时间。那帖子本身也有互动吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
