      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，帖子要有POST_REACTIONS表，记录用户对帖子的反应，比如点赞、收藏、转发这种。需要reaction_type枚举字段。POSTS表里我也加个reaction_count冗余字段。",
      "elements_involved": [
